  <section id="about" class="about">
    <h2>About Us</h2>
    <p>The Heron Brass Quintet is a dynamic chamber ensemble made up of talented young brass players dedicated to exploring the vast brass quintet repertoire. Formed in London, the group has already made an impact through performances in prestigious venues and festivals across the UK and abroad.</p>
    <p>With a repertoire spanning Renaissance transcriptions to contemporary works, Heron Brass seeks to showcase the versatility of brass instruments, captivating audiences with a unique blend of precision, power, and artistry.</p>
    <p>The ensemble recently reached the semifinal round of the Royal Overseas League competition and continues to expand its presence through concerts, competitions, and educational projects.</p>
  </section>

